; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/linux/hardinfo.md

% hardinfo, linux

# Start `hardinfo`
hardinfo

# Print report to `stdout`
hardinfo <__r___generate_report_>

# Save report to HTML file
hardinfo <__r___generate_report_> <__f___report_format_> html > hardinfo.html
